xx.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_WORKER_HANGARMECHANIC_: This outfit is worn by mechanics working in the hangar. They have access to the lower floors of the hangar, and can interact with the aircraft without drawing attention.
xx.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_WORKER_YACHTCREW_M_HPA: This outfit is worn by waiters and attendants aboard the yacht. They can access most non-private areas, as well as the bar. They can also tamper with food without drawing attention.
xx.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_WORKER_ENGINEER_M_HPA1: This outfit is worn by mechanics aboard the yacht. They can access quay areas, as well as the lower decks of the yacht.
xx.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_GUARD_SECURITY_M_HPA75: This outfit is worn by security staff outside the hangar. They can access all external areas, as well as the first floor. Additionally, they may carry weapons.
xx.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_GUARD_GENERICSECURITY_: This outfit is worn by security staff assigned to protect guests aboard the yacht. They can access most areas, and may carry weapons.
xx.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_GUARD_SOVIETSOLDIER_M_: This outfit is worn by Soviet soldiers assigned to the Cuban airbase. They can access all areas, and may be armed.
xx.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_GUARD_BODYGUARD_M_HPA2: This outfit is worn by bodyguards. Bodyguards may be armed, and can access most areas.
xx.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_UNIQUE_KGBCONTACT_M_HP: This outfit is worn by a high-ranking KGB officer. In keeping with his high rank, he can access most areas, and may carry weapons.

en.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_GUARD_SECURITY_M_HPA75: This outfit is worn by security staff outside the hangar. They can access all external areas including the first floor. Additionally, they may carry weapons.
en.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_GUARD_GENERICSECURITY_: This outfit is worn by security staff assigned to protect guests aboard the yacht. They can access most areas, and may carry weapons.

fr.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_WORKER_HANGARMECHANIC_: Cette tenue est portée par les mécaniciens qui travaillent dans le hangar. Ils ont accès aux étages inférieurs et peuvent interagir avec l'avion sans attirer l'attention.
fr.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_WORKER_YACHTCREW_M_HPA: Cette tenue est portée par les serveurs et les membres d'équipage à bord du yacht. Ils ont accès à la plupart des zones non privées et au bar, et peuvent manipuler la nourriture sans attirer l'attention.
fr.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_WORKER_ENGINEER_M_HPA1: Cette tenue est portée par les mécaniciens à bord du yacht. Ils ont accès aux quais et aux ponts inférieurs du bateau.
fr.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_GUARD_SECURITY_M_HPA75: Cette tenue est portée par les agents de sécurité en dehors du hangar. Ils ont accès à toutes les zones extérieures et peuvent également porter une arme.
fr.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_GUARD_JASPERBODYGUARD_: Garde du corps de Jasper Knight
fr.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_GUARD_GENERICSECURITY_: Cette tenue est portée par les agents de sécurité chargés de protéger les invités à bord du yacht. Ils ont accès à la plupart des zones et peuvent porter une arme.
fr.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_GUARD_SOVIETSOLDIER_M_: Cette tenue est portée par les soldats soviétiques assignés à la base aérienne cubaine. Ils ont accès à la plupart des zones et peuvent porter une arme.
fr.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_GUARD_BODYGUARD_M_HPA2: Cette tenue est portée par les gardes du corps. Ils ont accès à la plupart des zones et peuvent porter une arme.
fr.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_UNIQUE_KGBCONTACT_M_HP: Cette tenue est portée par un officier du KGB. Son grade élevé lui ouvre l'accès à la plupart des zones et lui permet de porter une arme.

it.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_WORKER_HANGARMECHANIC_: Abiti indossati dai meccanici che lavorano nell'hangar. Hanno accesso ai piani inferiori della struttura e possono interagire con il velivolo senza destare sospetti.
it.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_WORKER_YACHTCREW_M_HPA: Abiti indossati dai camerieri e dagli assistenti presenti a bordo dello yacht. Hanno accesso alla maggior parte delle aree non riservate, tra cui il bar. Inoltre, possono interagire con il cibo senza destare sospetti.
it.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_WORKER_ENGINEER_M_HPA1: Abiti indossati dai meccanici presenti a bordo dello yacht. Hanno accesso alle zone di attracco e ai ponti inferiori dell'imbarcazione.
it.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_GUARD_SECURITY_M_HPA75: Questi abiti sono indossati dal personale di sicurezza presente al di fuori dell'hangar. Hanno accesso a tutte le zone esterne, incluso il primo piano. In aggiunta, possono girare armati.
it.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_GUARD_JASPERBODYGUARD_: Guardia del corpo di Jasper Knight
it.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_GUARD_GENERICSECURITY_: Abiti indossati dal personale di sicurezza incaricato di proteggere gli ospiti dello yacht. Hanno accesso alla maggior parte delle aree e possono girare armati.
it.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_GUARD_SOVIETSOLDIER_M_: Questi abiti sono indossati dai soldati sovietici che presidiano la base aerea cubana. Hanno accesso a tutte le zone e possono girare armati.
it.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_GUARD_BODYGUARD_M_HPA2: Abiti indossati dalle guardie del corpo. Hanno accesso alla maggior parte delle aree e possono girare armati.
it.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_UNIQUE_KGBCONTACT_M_HP: Abiti indossati da un alto ufficiale del KGB. Il suo grado gli permette di accedere alla maggior parte delle aree e di girare armato.

de.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_WORKER_HANGARMECHANIC_: Dieses Outfit tragen die Mechaniker innerhalb des Hangars. Sie haben Zugang zu den unteren Etagen des Hangars und können mit dem Flugzeug interagieren, ohne Aufmerksamkeit zu erregen.
de.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_WORKER_YACHTCREW_M_HPA: Die Uniform der Kellner und Angestellten an Bord der Jacht. Diese haben Zugang zu den meisten öffentlichen Bereichen, einschließlich der Bar. Außerdem können sie mit Lebensmitteln hantieren, ohne Aufmerksamkeit zu erregen.
de.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_WORKER_ENGINEER_M_HPA1: Dieses Outfit tragen die Mechaniker an Bord der Jacht. Sie haben Zugang zum Kai-Bereich und zu den unteren Decks der Jacht.
de.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_GUARD_SECURITY_M_HPA75: Alle Sicherheitsleute außerhalb des Hangars tragen diese Uniform. Sie haben Zugang zu allen Außenbereichen sowie zum ersten Stock und dürfen Waffen tragen.
de.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_GUARD_GENERICSECURITY_: Die für den Schutz der Gäste an Bord der Jacht verantwortlichen Sicherheitsleute tragen diese Uniform. Sie haben Zugang zu den meisten Bereichen und dürfen Waffen tragen.
de.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_GUARD_SOVIETSOLDIER_M_: Die Uniform der auf dem kubanischen Flugfeld stationierten sowjetischen Soldaten. Sie haben Zugang zu den allen Bereichen und dürfen Waffen tragen.
de.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_GUARD_BODYGUARD_M_HPA2: Leibwächter tragen dieses Outfit. Sie dürfen Waffen tragen und haben Zugang zu den meisten Bereichen.
de.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_UNIQUE_KGBCONTACT_M_HP: Dies ist die Uniform eines hochrangigen KGB-Offiziers. Aufgrund seines Rangs hat er Zugang zu den meisten Bereichen und ist unter Umständen bewaffnet.

es.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_WORKER_HANGARMECHANIC_: Los mecánicos que trabajan en el hangar llevan este atuendo. Tienen acceso a las plantas bajas del hangar y pueden manipular el avión sin llamar la atención.
es.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_WORKER_YACHTCREW_M_HPA: Los camareros y asistentes a bordo del yate llevan este atuendo. Pueden acceder a la mayoría de zonas no privadas, además del bar. También pueden manipular comida sin llamar la atención.
es.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_WORKER_ENGINEER_M_HPA1: Los mecánicos a bordo del yate llevan este atuendo. Pueden acceder a las zonas del muelle, además de las cubiertas inferiores del yate.
es.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_GUARD_SECURITY_M_HPA75: El personal de seguridad de fuera del hangar lleva este atuendo. Pueden acceder a todas las zonas exteriores, incluido el primer piso, y llevar armas.
es.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_GUARD_GENERICSECURITY_: El personal de seguridad asignado para proteger a los invitados a bordo del yate lleva este traje. Pueden acceder a la mayoría de zonas y llevar armas.
es.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_GUARD_SOVIETSOLDIER_M_: Los soldados soviéticos asignados a la base aérea cubana llevan este atuendo. Pueden acceder a todas las zonas y llevar armas.
es.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_GUARD_BODYGUARD_M_HPA2: Los guardaespaldas llevan este atuendo. Pueden ir armados y acceder a la mayoría de zonas.
es.OUTFITS_GREENLAND_UNIQUE_KGBCONTACT_M_HP: Un agente de alto rango de la KGB lleva este atuendo. Por su alto rango puede acceder a la mayoría de zonas y llevar armas.
